data.description: It's time to come home to this wonderful home in the neighborhood of Carbonton Heights, which has easy access to US Hwy 1 & Hwy 421. Large lot containing .72 acres. When you enter the home check out the quality workmanship done throughout & the warm feeling of being "HOME". As the saying goes, this home has great "bones"! The finish on all the woodwork is extraordinaire! The first bedroom has a handicap bath which includes a walk-in shower & whirlpool tub, wide hallway & double closets with cedar lining. It also has a wall gas heater for winter comfort. This could also be a Master Suite, In-law suite or separate apartment. There are three additional bedrooms & an additional room for office, sewing, crafts, etc. A large living/family room with a fireplace for cozy nights, a combo kitchen/dining with lots of cabinets. New Roof & Water Heater.  HVAC 9 years.  Call for an appointment today!
